    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who make decorative paper, such as wallpaper, printed from wood blocks and colored by hand. This was a profession, for example, in 15th-century France.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
